posts.title:
A woman and her husband were refused service at the 
@SmoothieKing
 on Jackson Ave in Ann Arbor, Michigan because employees claimed that they felt uncomfortable with her husband's Trump hoodie.

I expect 
@SmoothieKing
 to take proper action and hope to hear from them soon.

